summary: Despite testing positive for a steroid twice, world number one tennis player Jannik Sinner will not face suspension. However, others have defended Sinner, citing the tribunal's decision and the fact that he did not intentionally take the banned substance. The situation has raised questions about the fairness of doping regulations and has also highlighted the challenges faced by athletes in managing their medications.

The game will also feature a new story campaign, which will take players across the war-torn planet of Pandora and beyond.

name: Phil Donahue
summary: Phil Donahue, a trailblazing talk show host who revolutionized daytime television, has passed away at the age of 88. Known for engaging his audiences in groundbreaking discussions, Donahue's show tackled taboo topics such as homosexuality and AIDS when few others were willing to. He became a significant LGBTQ+ ally, using his platform to foster understanding and challenge societal norms. Donahue's pioneering work has left an indelible mark on the television industry, inspiring a genre of shows that continue to inform and engage viewers to this day.

summary: Jasmine Crockett, a Texas state representative, made a speech at the Democratic National Convention (DNC) in which she highlighted the stark contrast between Joe Biden and his running mate, Kamala Harris, and President Donald Trump. She also spoke about her own personal encounter with Harris, describing her as a compassionate and empathetic leader. Crockett's speech was widely praised, with many commentators labeling her a rising star in the Democratic Party.

name: Epic
summary: Epic Games has expanded its reach by launching its game store on mobile devices, offering an alternative to the Apple and Google app stores. Despite legal challenges with Apple over its control of the iOS ecosystem, Epic continues to challenge monopolies in the industry. The company hosted a large gathering in Madison and has also made its alternative app store, AltStore, available for free in Europe. The legal battle with Apple over the removal of Fortnite from the iOS app store continues in the US, while the game has returned to Apple devices in Europe and Android devices globally. Epic Systems, known for its healthcare software, is urging its clients to adopt a new federal network for sharing medical records. Meanwhile, a judge in a different case has expressed a willingness to break down barriers to competition in Google's app store.

name: Jill Biden
summary: In her speech at the Democratic National Convention (DNC) on Monday, First Lady Jill Biden paid tribute to her husband, President Joe Biden. Her appearance marked a significant milestone for her as first lady and honored the President's legacy. Biden's speech also signaled the beginning of a farewell tour as she praised his character and decision-making, including his choice to withdraw from the 2024 race. Her speech was accompanied by a powerful fashion statement in a lilac Ralph Lauren dress. The couple is expected to deliver a "strong case" for Vice President Kamala Harris's reelection during the DNC's concluding night.
